it.emarolab.scene_identification_tracking.semanticSceneLibrary.objects

Class Semantics.MappingResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.emarolab.scene_identification_tracking.semanticSceneLibrary.objects.Semantics.MappingResult
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Semantics.ReadingResult, Semantics.WritingResult
    Enclosing interface:
    Semantics

    public abstract static class Semantics.MappingResult
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements the possible results state in common between #ReadingResult and #WritingResult.

    In particular this class manages the base result implementation and following results states:

    • ERROR: occurred during java computation,
    • INCONSISTENT: generated by the semantic reasoner,
    • NOT CHANGED: the semantic and java structure is up to dated.

    REMARK: extending class must have static state fields bigger than NOT_CHANGED.

    File: it.emarolab.scene_identification_tracking.semanticSceneLibrary.objects.Semantics
